Consequence_Description:
The two victims had very serious burns.&amp;nbsp; The first victim had burns in
his face, arms and legs. Almost 60 % of his body was very seriously
burned and his life was at risk for several weeks. The second victim,
had burns on his face and one of his arms. His situation was not
critical.&lt;br&gt;
Four months after the accident the second victim could resume his job and the first victim had left the hospital.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Affected Area: Affected Area: installation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
